data.description: This (3) bedroom (2) bathroom home is the one you have been looking for! Located a brisk 7 min. from the highly desirable Live Oak School District! This perfectly maintained home includes an open floor-plan that features luxurious vinyl plank  flooring in all main living areas, tile in wet areas, and carpeted bedrooms. Large lot with large shed included! Schedule a showing to see your next home. Huge walk-in closet in the primary bedroom, extra large pantry and laundry room. Attic has plenty of space for storage.
